Scientology has seemingly remained a secret since the start of its existence in the 1950's. It is not often that we as a society hear many things about this 'religion' unless, perhaps, negative comments in association with a 'cult'. I decided to dive head first into the process of 'joining' along with my homie ​⁠‪@3rdeyeomen596 ‬ , where we have attempted to journalise footage that not many have successfully obtained. This is based off OUR own experience in our time in the Church of Scientology closest to us. 

   This is part 2/2 of the series and if you haven't checked out part 1, please do so as these took months to make. I look forward to sharing similar sidequest X commentary content with y'all. PEACE!

episodes.title: I Secretly Joined A Cult And No-One Knew…
episodes.description:
Having been around for decades, what goes on inside Scientology has remained nothing short of a mystery. There has been VERY FEW instances of people ‘joining’ this community and being able to release any visuals or info. We decided to journalize OUR own experience with attending these meetings & events as well as completing and getting an insight on tests, audits, events, purification, and interviews with the Sea Org. Time is money, though Scientology is practically a Religion that lets you level up based on your financial contributions to the church, so here’s an inside view of how much TIME we spent in our City’s brand new Church Of Scientology…
